# Implementation Plan - Phase 4 Continuation: Enrollment & Learning Flow

This plan outlines the design and files to complete the remaining tasks in Phase 4: **Curriculum Guardrails**, **Paid Course Enrollment Verification**, **Completed Lessons Recovery**, and **ReportLab-based PDF Certificate Generation**.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> - **Certificate Generation Timing**: Certificates will be generated synchronously upon marking the final lesson as complete (achieving 100% progress). This avoids complexity without Celery workers, as generating a PDF with ReportLab is fast (typically <100ms).
> - **PDF Delivery**: Django's static media handlers will serve the certificate PDF directly to the student in the browser via dynamic secure links returned by the enrollment API.

