  - Include borders, an elegant title ("Certificate of Completion"), the student's full username/name, the course title, date of issuance, and a unique `certificate_code` for verification.
  - Save the output PDF directly to the `pdf_file` attribute on a newly created `Certificate` record.

#### [MODIFY] [views.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/payments/views.py) (Triggering)
